    "body": "Thanks for the report!\r\n\r\nIt's not a bug though. You are using solc 0.7.6 and back then the `@notice` tag was not allowed on non-public state variables. This changed in 0.8.4 and now it's allowed. If you want to use `@notice` like this, please update to a newer compiler version.",
